        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size:22px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500;">Israel-Iran Attack Plans Leaked</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopolitics.world/email/images/gp-oct-22-1.jpg" alt="Israel-Iran Attack Plans Leaked" href="https://www.geopolitics.world" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">The US is currently investigating a leak of highly <a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/10/19/politics/us-israel-iran-intelligence-documents/index.html" target="_blank">classified intelligence</a> regarding Israel‚Äôs preparations for a potential strike on Iran. These documents, marked ‚Äútop secret‚Äù and shared among ‚Äú<a href="https://privacyinternational.org/learn/five-eyes" target="_blank">Five Eyes</a>‚Äù allies, were first posted on Telegram by the ‚Äú<a href="https://t.me/s/Middle_East_Spectator" target="_blank">Middle East Spectator</a>‚Äù account. They detail Israeli military movements and exercises, hinting at plans for retaliation after Iran‚Äôs <a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/10/01/politics/iran-missile-attack-israel/index.html" target="_blank">missile barrage</a> on October 1.</p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">This leak raises alarm about US-Israeli trust and coordination, especially at such a sensitive time in their relations. US authorities are working to determine how the leak occurred. This could make the US re-evaluate how much assistance it might be willing to give Israel in the future. Meanwhile, Iran is bracing for Israeli retaliation by courting as many allies as it can. Iran could start to look towards Russia <a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2024/10/21/iran-aided-russia-against-ukraine-now-it-needs-to-call-in-the-favor.html" target="_blank">for a favor</a> in return for the missiles they provided them to strike Ukraine.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
